{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act12side", "eventName": "多索雷斯假日", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DH-9", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "鼠膽龍威", "storyInfo": "陳等人聯手擊敗了潘喬。坎黛拉的做法卻出乎了大家的意料。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chasing_intro", "key": "$chasing_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G09"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1", "name2": "avg_npc_203_1#5"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1", "name2": "avg_npc_203_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，快看，那邊被追趕的是老陳和林小姐吧？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#5"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1", "name2": "avg_npc_203_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，兩位世侄，了不起，真是了不起......", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1", "name2": "avg_npc_203_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們快去救......", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#5"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 3.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "忽然，已經駛到距離海岸不遠處的遊輪上發出了巨大的爆炸聲。"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "20_I06", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"xstrength": 3.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 2.0, "randomness": 100.0, "fadeout": "false", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你搞了什麼東西？", "name": "陳"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一點驚喜。", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是問你，救完人之後幹什麼嗎？", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然我也同意直接走人，但是我想起我身上還有炸彈。", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是就給他們多留了一點驚喜。", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "陳"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喝一杯？", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還真是有雅興。", "name": "陳"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開出來的時候才看到，就稍微擺了一下。", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無聊。", "name": "陳"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無趣。", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "陳"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道你是不是故意的。", "name": "陳"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你忘了？“而當你接過他們的班時，你不能只走他們的老路。”", "name": "陳"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說這段話的時候，我們的通訊還沒有斷開。", "name": "陳"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，你老實告訴我，那件事裡，你沒有做我所想的那些事，對嗎？", "name": "陳"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......到岸了。", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.01, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 10.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#6", "fadetime": 0.2}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你輸了，老頭。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#6"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#8"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幫助坎黛拉那個女人，小姑娘，你們不理解自己做了什麼。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#8"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你做得好啊，老潘喬。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_193"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坎黛拉！", "name": "船長手下"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_193"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "住手。我們已經輸了。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#8"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明智的選擇，老潘喬。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來，坐。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坎黛拉，你想幹什麼？", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#8"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看不懂嗎？請你吃飯。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#3", "fadetime": 0.3}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潘喬冷哼一聲，卻還是坐在了坎黛拉的對面。"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別的人在這個時候恐怕已經嚇破膽了，我就是看中你這一點，老潘喬。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當不起。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#8"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經輸了，你沒有把我抓起來，還請我坐在這裡，你究竟想幹什麼？羞辱我？", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#8"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聊一聊，老潘喬。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "用埃內斯托來分散我的注意力，讓手下參加比賽，透過比賽在城市各處埋好炸彈。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後在第三輪前夕發難，挾持船上的富豪和權貴讓我不能輕舉妄動。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不得不說，這一次，可能是我最接近失去這座城市的一次了。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*玻利瓦爾俚語*，我真是不明白，坎黛拉，為了這一次的計畫，我和我的手下準備了多少個日日夜夜。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#8"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你，你只是恰好請了兩個什麼都不知道的外地人，恰好把這件事交給她們。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#8"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而她們，她們居然就正好破壞了我的計畫！！！", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#8"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼贏的是你這樣的人？", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#8"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我贏了？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在說什麼，潘喬，我的老潘喬，看來你在我的城市裡待了太久，連我是什麼人都忘了。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者說，你從未瞭解過我。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的對手從來都不是我，你也沒有輸給我。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你只是失敗了，就這麼簡單。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在最厭惡的城市中生活了十數年，說著痛恨三方政府的話，卻為了推翻我而不得不接受其中一家的資助。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我猜猜，是萊塔尼亞的某一位吧，啊，我甚至能大概想到是哪一位。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我，老潘喬，你是怎麼想的，居然向那些吃人不吐骨頭的傢伙尋求幫助。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#8"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，意思是，你學會了忍辱負重。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你為什麼不向我搖尾乞憐呢？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼知道我不會幫助你？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說真的，老潘喬，要是你來求我，我說不定真的會給你人和錢去打你最愛的戰爭。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你最後贏了，那這座城市也會投靠你。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我覺得不會有比這更有吸引力的方案了。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這輩子都不可能向你低頭。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#8"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，你這種人啊，就是在這方面太頑固了。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們這樣的人，對於完整，獨立這樣的詞彙總是有著一種不切實際的期待。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們妄想著有一種氣節會將你們聯繫起來，你們追尋著一種象徵能夠讓你們團結其下。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而事實上，玻利瓦爾從一開始就沒有獨立過，既然沒有歷史，又談何氣節，談何象徵？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你成功了，你所建立的玻利瓦爾真的是你想像中的玻利瓦爾嗎？我看不見得。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管你怎麼說，我所想的從一開始就只是終結戰爭，讓玻利瓦爾和平。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#8"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天我失敗了，我認栽，坎黛拉。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#8"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是你記住，我的事業或許不是正義的，但我至少要比你正義！", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#8"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，對不起，瞧我，又把你和你背後的人混為一談了。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是我所描述的那類人，你發自內心地想要拯救這個國家，所以你能夠坐在這裡。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，作為對你失敗的懲罰，我還是把你當做他們的代表吧，這樣說起來比較方便。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從來沒有自詡過正義，我親愛的老潘喬。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不關心三方政府想幹什麼，我也不關心你們的玻利瓦爾。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事實上，你說我沉迷於這座城市，這也是錯誤的，我不關心這座城市。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我關心的是這座城市代表的意義。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "意義？娛樂到死就是你在乎的意義？", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#8"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_198_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，你這樣的老頑固，永遠不懂金錢的意義。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，把這個老東西帶下去吧，我之後再和他聊聊。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剩下那些抵抗的，你們應該知道怎麼處理吧。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_207"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "護衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_207"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖嘖，這場面，鴻門宴也不過如此了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#5"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在旁邊看著都感覺頭皮發麻。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#5"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感覺和以前爸爸跟爺爺吃飯時的氣氛似的，我每次都受不了。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星熊？！", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#4"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "詩懷雅？！", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#4"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗨。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們兩個身上都是水，趕緊擦擦吧。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#7"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#4"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們怎麼會在這裡？！", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#4"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈，這就說來話長了。之後吃飯的時候慢慢說吧。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，事情變成這樣，我可沒胃口吃飯。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩位世侄，瞧我，光顧著和老潘喬說話，居然把最大的功臣給冷落了。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，那邊的，趕緊拉兩架無人機過來，燈光也打過來！", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們做得漂亮，實在是太漂亮了。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "魏彥吾真是讓我認識了兩個大好後輩。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也為這場大獎賽貢獻了一個精彩絕倫的收尾。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#4"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大獎賽？收尾？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#4"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，不出意外的話，現在應該有很多人正坐在電視前看著你我。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然船內發生的事我們沒有拍到，但是陳世侄你在甲板上和潘喬對峙的那一幕，一定深深印在了所有人的心中。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，他們必然都在為你們歡呼。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您曾經說過，只要有您在，就不會有任何人威脅到這座城市。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，沒錯，這句話有什麼問題嗎？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道眼前發生的事就不算威脅？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈，陳世侄，你還是太年輕了。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼是威脅？是這座城市被夷平？是這座城市裡的人死光了？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都不是，都不是，陳世侄。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真正的威脅是人們不再有欲望，是人們不再追求享樂。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你也做了這麼多年警察，你認為有可能嗎，陳世侄？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，你的表情告訴了我你的答案。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看，你也明白，答案是不可能。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而只要答案是不可能，這座城市就將永遠存在，多索雷斯沒了，還會有特雷索雷斯。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論幾座，我都能給你造出來。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，這並不能掩蓋你們是這座城市的英雄的事實。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噢，瞧我，忘了這件事。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宴會準備好了沒有？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_207"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "基本準備好了。", "name": "護衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_207"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的話筒呢......哦，在這。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$fesedm_intro", "key": "$fesedm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳，親愛的市民們，遊客們，無論你此時身在電視機前，還是依然留在沙灘上。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我非常榮幸地向你們介紹本次極限鐵人大獎賽的最終勝利者，同時也是拯救了這座城市的英雄。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來自龍門的兩位女俠——陳暉潔，林雨霞！", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "非常感謝老潘喬用自己的親身行動為我們帶來的表演！", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來，我們將在沙灘上舉辦宴會，歡迎所有人來參與！", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$livecrowd"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}